the Senate and in the House, giving them the

00:38:35.840 --> 00:38:41.940
kinds of arguments they need. We have to be
prepared with lawsuits to block efforts. Remember,

00:38:41.940 --> 00:38:46.760
it's hard to pass legislation, but it’s
equally hard to get rid of legislation.

00:38:46.760 --> 00:38:51.079
And we're specialists at defending the things
that are important to us.

00:38:51.079 --> 00:38:58.410
The third, in terms of the message, we think
we will win the message. If they go after

00:38:58.410 --> 00:39:03.549
Lisa Jackson and the laws that protect our
health, I think that we will win the message

00:39:03.549 --> 00:39:08.740
and we will gain back our losses in the next
election.

00:39:08.740 --> 00:39:14.890
There are other things that are going on here
that are very important. I look at the Department

00:39:14.890 --> 00:39:21.710
of Energy. It has 90,000,000 dollars that
it is spending on efficiency and new technology,

00:39:21.710 --> 00:39:27.559
