Midwest. They're gonna be the battleground

00:39:33.030 --> 00:39:38.400
states of the next election. If the battery
companies and the car companies do grow, as

00:39:38.400 --> 00:39:45.920
one would expect, and people like the folks
at NRDC, we've just built a new office in

00:39:45.920 --> 00:39:51.579
Chicago. That office in Chicago is looking
at the coal power plants; it’s looking at

00:39:51.579 --> 00:39:55.460
the battery companies as supporters of theirs.

00:39:55.460 --> 00:40:01.870
We're gonna build a new front in the rust
belt, because without the rust best, we're

00:40:01.870 --> 00:40:05.609
never gonna be able to get a climate bill
passed in this country.

00:40:05.609 --> 00:40:13.079
