what we need to do and I would just say that

00:40:13.079 --> 00:40:23.720
we watched the Proposition 23, and that fight
over "would we have a climate bill here in

00:40:23.720 --> 00:40:25.329
California" was absolutely critical.

00:40:25.329 --> 00:40:32.819
Well, what was really critical was that the
folks from Google and from Silicon Valley

00:40:32.819 --> 00:40:41.670
stepped into the fight and became major players
in defending AB 32. And that's a lesson, a

00:40:41.670 --> 00:40:47.539
victory, a major victory, that I think will
not be lost on the folks who were doing this

00:40:47.539 --> 00:40:54.309
kind of work, because for it to succeed, they
have to have a regulatory framework that works.

00:40:54.309 --> 00:41:00.270
